{"tid":428232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[超突發]大埔女子墮樓撞簷篷　慘遭分屍","createTime":"2017-10-08T02:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T14:20:27.000Z","uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"85acb9999eca4e4989248e90edf93251b106082d","tid":428232,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"大埔發生墮樓事件。今晨8時許，大埔太和邨翠和樓一名女子突然由高處墮下，街坊聞聲發現報警求助。消防員及救護員到場證實女子經已不治，相信女子墮樓時撞向簷篷邊，慘遭分屍，部分身軀擱在簷篷上，部分肢體斷開跌在地面，警方正調查其身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171008/bkn-20171008091450876-1008_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171008%2Fbkn-20171008091450876-1008_00822_001.html&d=tQU83yfXv3yolmsGgYcyQzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8c669349\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171008/bkn-20171008091450876-1008_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171008/photo/bkn-20171008091450876-1008_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171008100050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171008%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171008091450876-1008_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171008100050&h=fb129458&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae4d1f37cd3aa320d6d4fe63bd2cfbda7b4d3189","tid":428232,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171008/photo/bkn-20171008091450876-1008_00822_001_04b.jpg?20171008100050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171008%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171008091450876-1008_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20171008100050&h=ffd53a85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"126e5a0b06823da789cae98ed38e586773490fb2","tid":428232,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj